divs: Sighting Detailsas i was about to leave for work i noticed something strange flying in from the north as it flew closer i started to realize it wasn't anyhting i have seen before it was a long tube looking object with windows or holes one of the two this object was tan colored and was flying in a straight path north to south and was flying below the clouds the clouds were not high in the sky so the object was pretty low now this object was not a plane because the object didn't have any wings i am just puzzled with what has been happening in the area lately truly bizarre
Summary: a long tan colored tube ufo with windows or holes
